.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding
2 different pets are kept: cat, pony
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country       |
| Sport         | sailing   | skateboarding |
| Pet     | pony    | cat     |

