The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the coach is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Hobby           | woodworking          | board-games    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 